1
00:00:02,114 --> 00:00:06,923
She did something that,
in our society, is unspeakable.

2
00:00:06,986 --> 00:00:09,458
She kissed a black man.

3
00:00:09,522 --> 00:00:13,796
Not an old uncle,

4
00:00:13,859 --> 00:00:16,999
but a strong, young Negro man.

5
00:00:20,033 --> 00:00:23,840
No code mattered to her
before she broke it,

6
00:00:23,903 --> 00:00:28,112
but it came crashing down
on her afterwards.

7
00:00:35,049 --> 00:00:39,257
The witnesses for the State,
with the exception of the
sheriff of Maycomb County.

8
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:42,694
have presented themselves
to you gentlemen, to this court...

9
00:00:44,559 --> 00:00:48,667
in the cynical confidence...

10
00:00:48,729 --> 00:00:52,704
that their testimony
would not be doubted.

11
00:00:52,767 --> 00:00:57,777
Confident that you gentlemen
would go along with them...

12
00:00:57,840 --> 00:01:01,514
on the assumption--

13
00:01:01,577 --> 00:01:03,681
the evil assumption--

14
00:01:03,745 --> 00:01:06,551
that all Negroes lie,

15
00:01:06,615 --> 00:01:09,821
all Negroes are basically
immoral beings,

16
00:01:09,885 --> 00:01:15,529
all Negro men are not
to be trusted around our women.

17
00:01:17,493 --> 00:01:22,804
An assumption that one associates
with minds of their caliber,

18
00:01:22,866 --> 00:01:27,642
and which is, in itself,
gentlemen, a lie,

19
00:01:30,107 --> 00:01:34,181
which I do not need
to point out to you.

20
00:01:39,617 --> 00:01:42,656
And so,

21
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:45,859
a quiet, humble,
respectable Negro,

22
00:01:45,923 --> 00:01:50,065
who has had the unmitigated
temerity...

23
00:01:50,128 --> 00:01:54,536
to feel sorry
for a white woman,

24
00:01:54,599 --> 00:02:00,511
has had to put his word
against two white people's.

25
00:02:04,943 --> 00:02:08,450
The defendant is not guilty,

26
00:02:08,513 --> 00:02:12,890
but somebody
in this courtroom is.

27
00:02:13,819 --> 00:02:16,992
Now, gentlemen,

28
00:02:17,056 --> 00:02:19,126
in this country,

29
00:02:19,191 --> 00:02:23,199
our courts are the great levelers.

30
00:02:23,263 --> 00:02:25,600
in our courts,

31
00:02:25,665 --> 00:02:31,109
all men are created equal.

32
00:02:32,673 --> 00:02:36,647
i'm no idealist
to believe firmly...

33
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:39,949
in the integrity of our courts
and of our jury system.

34
00:02:40,013 --> 00:02:44,922
That's no ideal to me.
That is a living, working reality !

